text: Willie B. Brown (June 18, 1940 – January 5, 2009) was an American politician who served in the New Jersey General Assembly from the 29th Legislative District from 1974 to 1998. He died of heart failure on January 5, 2009, in Edison, New Jersey at age 68. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:2009 deaths Category:Members of the New Jersey General Assembly Category:New Jersey Democrats
title: Willie B. Brown
